&lt;li&gt;Provide technical guidance on design concepts (risk vs. cost vs. performance)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support manufacturing to validate and verify that designs meet requirements and specifications&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
