&lt;li&gt;Machined metal&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with the manufacturing of composite parts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of FAA aircraft certification requirements for Part 23 aircraft&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with PDM systems&lt;/li&gt;
