&lt;li&gt;Broad experience across a range of airframe structures (fuselage, wing, pylons, empennage)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with composite laminate definition in FiberSim&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
