&lt;li&gt;Proficiency with CAD tools (NX, CATIA, CREO, or equivalent) for viewing and validating models and drawings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with Product Lifecycle Management (PLM) systems such as Teamcenter, Windchill, or Enovia&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong knowledge of ASME Y14.5 GD&amp;amp;T and ASME Y14 drafting standards&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to interpret engineering drawings, CAD models, and metadata accurately&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with tolerance analysis and drawing release processes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic understanding of configuration management concepts (effectivity, baselines, change control)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effective written and verbal communication skills to document fin

