&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You will report to Archer&#39;s Head of Government Affairs to ensure Archer’s mission is understood and supported by key policymakers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
